<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etwieoft
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der gült <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        die ir uns auf <app>
<note><q type="date">sand Michelstag
                                        <expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan></q>29.09.1415</note>
</app>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>fallen</expan> seyt, uns die zu beczaln, des noch niht
                                <expan>bescheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ist.
                            <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch aber, daz ir
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet und uns des niht lenger
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehet</expan>, daz wir der gült beczalt
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, wan uns niht füklich ist, daz wir es
                                <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> steen <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Geschech des niht, so <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bürg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>zusprech<ex>en</ex></expan> und manen nach
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> briefs sag, wie
                            <expan>ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir es tun. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
